Interface TransferCopier

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseObject, Comparable<TransferCopier>, Value<TransferCopier>, VmReflected
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BaseFutureTransferCopier

    @ReflectionManual
public interface TransferCopier
extends BaseObject, Value<TransferCopier>, Comparable<TransferCopier>
    An object whose duty is to provide any number of equal buffers.
